{"tid":659934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每日平均輸入「專才」112人?! 直逼單程証150限額!!","createTime":"2018-05-10T09:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T10:44:05.000Z","uid":53060,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"40d3c142250e2d52108ce284f843180b90e81d55","tid":659934,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"10/05/2018 09:58<br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社１０日專訊》據政府向立法會提交的文件顯示，本港由２００８年至今年３月，通過<span style=\"color: red;\">「一般就業政策」、「輸入內地人才計劃」及「優秀人才入境計劃」</span>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">引入逾４０﹒７萬名外地專才</span></span></strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> (407,000/365/10 = 111.5人/日)</span>，當中３個計劃的引入人數佔比分別約為７７％、２２％及１％。<br />\n<br />\n　　文件顯示，「輸入內地人才計劃」的獲批人數，去年按年升１９％至１﹒２４萬人，創出新高，引入的人才中，主要來自「學術研究及教育」、「建築╱測量」及「金融服務」行業，約十年間分別有２﹒６２萬、２﹒２萬和１﹒２３萬人；而資訊科技業的專才則只有２７９０人，每年平均不到３００人。<br />\n<br />\n　　至於透過「優秀人才入境計劃」引人的人才，去年數字按年升５０﹒６％至４１１人，為２００９年以來最高。若單計去年的數字，當中大部分來自「金融及會計服務」及「資訊科技╱電訊」業，分別有１１４和７６人、佔整體約２７﹒７％及１８﹒５％。（ｄｌ）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN280510516&amp;page=1&amp;category=latest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fnewsid%3DETN280510516%26page%3D1%26category%3Dlatest&d=GoifjXAQR2dURKEittJIZdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=60a6d161\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN280510516&amp;page=1&amp;category=latest</a>"},{"pid":"2abc36b62e0f9e8ca78c723fc87245bc05bece39","tid":659934,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:26:13.000Z","msg":"樓價GoGoGo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f1eafd58a54f2d0f77477994bdbaecb8a0c5c9","tid":659934,"uid":15815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"又多個理由取消香港關係法🤦🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"c11b81ff9fa0efbd345b08995dfaa16ba90a